item.title: SoftLayer_Network_Storage_Credential
item.description: SoftLayer_Network_Storage_Credential Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Network_Storage_Credential data type will give you an overview of the usernames that are currently attached to your storage device. Local accountId This is the account id associated with the volume. Type: string createDate This is the data that the record was created in the table. Type: dateTime id Type: integer modifyDate This is the date that the record was last updated in the table.
